{
  "texts": [
    "or refusals, e.g., 'I'm sorry, but I cannot provide a response'.",
    "Inspired byRöttger et al. (2024)",
    ", we employ 1) a rule-based method and 2) a zero-shot stance detector to classify refusal in LLM responses.",
    "For rule-based refusal classification, we flag any LLM response as refusal that starts with, e.g., 'I'm sorry', 'I don't think it's appropriate', etc.",
    "To this end, we expand the list of refusal markers suggested byRöttger et al. (2024)"
  ]
}